{"id":486,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":87,"title":"87. A Birth","subtitle":"","level":"B1","parts":9,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/87-a-birth.486/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/87-a-birth-2022-03-07-21-34-29/0-87-a-birth.mp3","transcript":"Have you heard about the good news in the Wallace family?\nNo, I've been out of town.\nMrs Wallace went into the hospital last night and gave birth to a baby girl seven hours later.\nThat's very good. But they already have a little girl, don't they?\nNo, they have a 5-year-old boy.\nSo they wanted a girl this time, right?\nYes, they wanted a girl for a long time.\nWas it natural childbirth?\nNo, she had to have a caesarean.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:49:06","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Have you heard about the good news in the Wallace family?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/87-a-birth-2022-03-07-21-34-29/1.mp3","time_start":2.32,"time_end":4.97},{"position":2,"content":"No, I've been out of town.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/87-a-birth-2022-03-07-21-34-29/2.mp3","time_start":4.97,"time_end":6.4},{"position":3,"content":"Mrs Wallace went into the hospital last night and gave birth to a baby girl seven hours later.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/87-a-birth-2022-03-07-21-34-29/3.mp3","time_start":6.42,"time_end":11.45},{"position":4,"content":"That's very good. But they already have a little girl, don't they?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/87-a-birth-2022-03-07-21-34-29/4.mp3","time_start":11.45,"time_end":14.4},{"position":5,"content":"No, they have a 5-year-old boy.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/87-a-birth-2022-03-07-21-34-29/5.mp3","time_start":14.4,"time_end":16.51},{"position":6,"content":"So they wanted a girl this time, right?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/87-a-birth-2022-03-07-21-34-29/6.mp3","time_start":16.51,"time_end":18.48},{"position":7,"content":"Yes, they wanted a girl for a long time.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/87-a-birth-2022-03-07-21-34-29/7.mp3","time_start":18.48,"time_end":21.39},{"position":8,"content":"Was it natural childbirth?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/87-a-birth-2022-03-07-21-34-29/8.mp3","time_start":21.42,"time_end":23.16},{"position":9,"content":"No, she had to have a caesarean.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/87-a-birth-2022-03-07-21-34-29/9.mp3","time_start":23.16,"time_end":25.43}]}